			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Idle AD for Alfira while she's staying in the camp. In the top set she's been recruited player and is happy and excited. In the bottom set she's mad at the player and doesn't want to be there - she just wants to go to sleep.&#xD;&#xA;ADs are enabled only for - recrutied Alfira, Alfira quit being a bard, and player broke her lute." />
